title: Number of choking-deaths in the U.S. 1945 to 2018
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of deaths, containing a total of 30 data points.
Overall Number of deaths has increased over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 1995 and 2000.
Maximum Number of deaths, about 5216.0 was reported at Year 2017
Minimum Number of deaths about 897.0 was reached at Year 1945
